com.printnode.api

Class Account

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.printnode.api.Account

  • public class Account
extends java.lang.Object
    Account object. When being used, will generally be created via the blank constructor. The other constructor is for CreateAccountJson, which requires firstname, lastname, email and password to be set.
